        "inactive": true
      },
      "date": "2012-07-30 03:44:48.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Abandoned\n\nAlex's http://review.whamcloud.com/3484 fixes the fsname problem as well as a few others.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
